ethemoglobin-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/120375/', '', 'Nesiritide, Vericiguat, Zinc sulfate, Diltiazem, Zinc acetate, Fluocinolone acetonide, Hydrocortisone, Fluocinonide, Zinc chloride, Prednisolone, Betamethasone, More', 'Zinc sulfate, Zinc acetate, Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluocinonide, Isosorbide dinitrate, Zinc chloride, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, Zinc gluconate, Tripelennamine, Clemastine, Pheniramine', 1767369485);
